winegame is a simple utility, written in Qt4, as a front-end to Wine.
It can set up a wine envs, and run game installation in one click.
License: GPLv3
Site: http://winegame.googlecode.com

============================================
Install deps:
Qt 4.6 (Core, Gui and Network modules)
fuseiso
notify-send/KDialog
winetricks
=========================================
Winetricks info:
Homepage: http://wiki.winehq.org/winetricks
Download url: http://tinyurl.com/winetricks
You can find ebuild for winetricks in os/gentoo/ subdirectory. Don`t forgot about digests.
=========================================
Directories info:
src - sources
src/l10n - translations
packages - WineGame packages
os - information for Linux distros (package managers)
desktop - image & FreeDesktop launcher
resources - QRC files
==========================================

